<plot>A small town boy, (Justin), picked on by locals for being slow, wants nothing more than a simple life and the love of the local beauty, (Rachel). Despite the disapproval of his father figure, (Mr Fisher), and the threats of Rachels current boyfriend, (Bobby), Justin continues his pursuit of her. This obsession changes Justin, and in the end he lets nothing stand in his way to have her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?521652</url></doc>
